extendedInfo.description: A funny and gorgeous puzzle game, theme of dessert, each couple pictures contain 3 differences, while you find out all 3, you will walk through the level. All delicious dessert include: candies, cookies, cakes, ice creams, very seductive! Can you figure out the differences?How fast can you find 3 differences between 2 photos?2 PHOTOS, 3 DIFFERENCES.Wonderful Dessert photos. Your power of observation sharpens as you search for the differences and advance through the modes. Time is not your friend and hints must be used wisely.âHow to PlayâFind the differences between the two pictures shown, then touch on either photo to mark the difference.
